World State (As Experienced by Players in Early Adventures):
Atmosphere: Localized strangeness. Stories of sacred groves where animals no longer go, of springs that have run foul with an unnatural taint. These are dismissed as local superstitions or isolated curses.
Party's First Encounter: The "Thornheart Grove" adventure is the party's first direct confrontation with this phase. They successfully reverse the corruption, proving it is possible and marking themselves as an unforeseen variable in the cult's ancient plan.

